title: Normal HOSE2237
treatment_protocol_ch1: Tumor specimens were obtained from 185 previously untreated late-stage (III–IV) high-grade ovarian cancer patients. A set of 10 normal ovarian surface epithelium (OSE) cytobrushing specimens were used as control
extract_protocol_ch1: Total RNA was isolated using the RNeasy Micro kit (Qiagen)
label_protocol_ch1: Labeled amplified RNA (aRNA) for microarray analysis was generated from tumor or OSE-derived total RNA using a single round of amplification
hyb_protocol: A 15 microgram aliquot of amplified biotinylated RNA was hybridized to a Human U133 Plus 2.0 GeneChip array (Affymetrix, Santa Clara, CA).
scan_protocol: Array images were acquired using a GeneChip Scanner 3000 (Affymetrix)
description: Gene expression data from ovarian surface epithelial cells
